image_1_text: a lovely house with tile floors, two nice sofas, and a view of a nice pool.
image_2_text: a nice sitting room in a lovely looking house, with two sofas and a two lights in the main sitting room.

image_1_text: a quaint looking bedroom with a chaise lounger, a comfy looking bed, and a nice large mirror.
image_2_text: this bedroom has a lovely chaise lounger, a comfy looking bed, a large mirror, a beautiful vase display with one vase balancing on top of another.

image_1_text: this hotel room has a nice view of the skyline, you can see a nice hill or small mountain in the back, as well as a pretty treeline.
image_2_text: this hotel room is facing a nice view of the skyline. behind the buildings you can see some nice trees, and behind the trees there appears to be a large tower looming over it all.

image_1_text: a nice tiled sitting room with a piano and a lovely seating area with what appears to be leather furniture.
image_2_text: this lovely tiled sitting room has a piano underneath a painting, and nice leather seats in the middle of the room. at  the back, by the sliding glass doors, is another piece of art, for collectibles.

image_1_text: this dining room is cozy and has a nice little table as well as plenty of natural light.
image_2_text: this dining room has a lovely view of the outside, as well as a small but comfortable looking table set. on the wall there is a quaint looking piece of art that almost looks like a puzzle piece.

image_1_text: this seating area or living room is comfy looking with two nice leather sofas set a top a nice wooden floor.
image_2_text: this living room has plenty of natural light that compliments the nice natural wood floors. the tv is quite small, and both the leather sofas appear to face it.

image_1_text: this child's room is very colorful. the bunk bed is white, but everything else in the room is exploding with colors.
image_2_text: the child's room is quite bright, from the yellow walls, to the lovely 6 drawer furniture module that has alternating colors. one pull knob is missing from the top blu drawer of the module.

image_1_text: this kitchen is lovely and quaint. nice tile floors accentuate the antique but modern look of the layout.
image_2_text: the cabinets in this kitchen are quite lovely and appear very antique yet modern as well. there are four shelves on each unit to the left and right of the range. at the top of both shelving units is a bowl on either side.

image_1_text: this room appears to be for a teen girl, the bed or lounger appears quite comfortable, and the room's color palette of cream and pink goes nicely together.
image_2_text: this teen girls room is very fashionable and the lovely pink desk compliments the cream of the furniture. on top of the pink desk appears to be a makeup case or something to that effect.

image_1_text: this tiled bathroom is cream in color, with brown accents set by the towels and the rug on the floor.
image_2_text: this lovely tiled bathroom is cream in color, and there are two faucets on the wall, each going into it's own basin, and each has it's own mirror above it.

image_1_text: this comfy cafe has large plush chairs and small tables. on top of each table is a nice candle.
image_2_text: each table in this lovely and small cafe has a small candle on top of it. there is also a small vase on the second table from center, it appears to be brown or black.

image_1_text: this living room has lovely natural wood floors and a nice l shaped sofa with cream cushions on top.
image_2_text: this lovely living room has natural wood floors and a nice l shaped soda adorned with cream cushions, and a black accent cushion as well.
